          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " To obtain the energy dependence of the Th-232(n,g)",
                " cross section, the B-10(n,a)Li-7 cross section curve",
                " to the excited state of Li-7 was used.",
                " Background in time of flight experiment was deter-",
                " mined by using notch filters of Na-23 and S-32.",
                " The energy dependence of the Th-232(n,g) cross",
                " section was also measured with Fe and Si filtered",
                " neutron beams."
